## Import Paths

Always use the `@/` alias for absolute imports:

```tsx
// correct
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"
import { useUser } from "@/hooks/useUser"
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"

// wrong - no relative imports for project files
import { Button } from "../../../components/ui/button"
```
